description: Record to support submission of GeneRIFs for a gene not in Gene (Acetobacter acidum-mucosum; Acetobacter agglutinans; Acetobacter alcoholophilus; Acetobacter kutzigianus; Acetobacter lovaniense; Acetobacter mobile; Acetobacter pasteurianus ascendens; Acetobacter pasteurianus orleanensis; Acetobacter pasteurianus paradoxus; Acetobacter pasteurianus subsp. orleanensis; Acetobacter rancens; Acetobacter turbidans; Acetobacter vini-aceti; Bacillus kuttingianum; Bacteriopsis pasteuriana; Bacterium kutzingianum; Bacterium pastorianum; Bacterium rancens; Bacterium vini-aceti; Mycoderma pasteurianum; Pseudomonas pomi; Ulvina pasteuriana.  Use when strain, subtype, isolate, etc. is unspecified, or when different from all specified ones in Gene.).
